text: Międzybórz may refer to the following places in Poland: *Międzybórz, also known as Międzybórz Sycowski, town in Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Międzybórz, Greater Poland Voivodeship (west-central Poland) *Międzybórz, Łódź Voivodeship (central Poland) *Międzybórz, Pomeranian Voivodeship (north Poland) == See also == *Medzhybizh, town in Western Ukraine (till 1795 Międzybórz in the Polish-Lithuanian Commonwealth), famous for Hassidism
title: Międzybórz (disambiguation)
